  <thing id="raCBFalAgD" name="Agent of Despair" description="A fallen's attacks can weaken a creature's resolve. Any creature that takes damage from a fallen's attacks must succeed at a DC 19 Will save or take a &#150;4 penalty on saving throws against fear. If a creature that has immunity to fear fails this saving throw, its immunity is temporarily suppressed. This effect lasts as long as a creature still suffers damage taken from a fallen's attacks. This effect is removed if the creature is healed of all damage inflicted by a fallen. The save DC is Charisma-based." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Attacks make it harder for target to resist fear.">
