  <thing id="raCBNocDom" name="Domination" description="As a standard action, Nocticula can crush a foe's will. The target must be visible to Nocticula and within 120 feet. It must succeed at a DC 43 Will save or fall instantly under Nocticula's influence as {i}dominate monster{/i} (CL 30th). If she uses domination against a humanoid creature, she may instead choose to use the ability as a swift action, and it functions as {i}dominate person{/i}. As long as the target is under this effect, it gains a +4 profane bonus on all saving throws against targets other than Nocticula." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Dominate creatures as {/i}dominate moster{/i} or {i}dominate person{/i}.">
