    <eval phase="Final" priority="20000">field[abSumm].text = &quot;Sting or hand crossbow-injury; {i}save{/i} Fort DC &quot; &amp; field[abDC].value &amp; &quot;; {i}frequency{/i} 1/round for 6 rounds; {i}effect{/i} 1d4 Wis drain plus paralysis for 1 round. Anyone who fails two consecutive saves against this poison is permanently blinded.&quot;

~ set livename to just poison

