  <thing id="raCBDevCor" name="Aura of Corruption" description="A devastator emanates an aura that bolsters chaotic evil outsiders. Any such creature with 15 or more Hit Dice within 60 feet of a devastator gains a +10 enhancement bonus to Strength and Charisma. In addition, the creature's spell resistance increases by 5. If such a creature doesn't already possess spell resistance, it gains spell resistance equal to 11 + its CR." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Aura bolsters chaotic evil outsiders." uniqueness="useronce">
